description: The demolition of Ipswich House, St. Norbert Road SE4 and construction of three to seven storey blocks/terraces, comprising a total of 37 one bedroom and 16 two bedroom self-contained flats, 9 three bedroom, 7 four bedroom and 2 five bedroom houses, together with associated landscaping, provision of bin and cycle stores, 11 car parking spaces and refurbishment of the under-croft at 1-12 Bessingham Walk, to provide additional parking, with access onto Aldersford Close.
